"Jot with Ayo Memopad" is a sleek and intuitive note-taking app built using React Native. This app allows users to easily jot down thoughts, ideas, and to-dos on the go. The app leverages SQLite as its primary storage system for fast and reliable data management, ensuring that notes are securely saved and quickly accessed. Additionally, it utilizes the Async Storage system for lightweight data storage, making the app more efficient and responsive. With a user-friendly interface and seamless performance, "Jot with Ayo Memopad" is the perfect tool for anyone looking to stay organized and productive.
